ness for profit education prek 12 schools international private public charter public school entrepreneurial start up foundations government public administration higher education nonprofit firms ngo's philanthropic public policy research explore careers in education such as administration advising & counseling community organizing communications consulting curriculum design development and fund raising education services support health human services human resources instructional design law lobbying advocacy marketing & public relations media technology policy analysis program management research evaluation teaching prek 12 & higher ed you may register with susedcareers post your job announcements and sign up for the career fair by clicking the students and alumni or employers button audience suse current students and alumni event category career services sponsor school of education contact name alice mccarty contact email alice mccarty stanford edu contact phone 650 723 0555 website susedcareers calendar news &amp events events in the spotlight school news press releases suse in the media stanford educator itunes u suse on youtube featured events march 20 screening of mitchell 20 and panel discussion 4 30 pm 6 45 pm ceras 100b april 5 school of education 2012 career fair registration is open 3 30 pm 6 00 pm tresidder union 2nd floor april 13 aera reception in vancouver bc 8 00 pm 10 00 pm the fairmont hotel vancouver event calendar stanford university school of education 485 lasuen mall stanford ca 94305 3096 tel 650 723 2109 copyright 2012 stanford university all rights reserved terms of use copyright complaints site map contact us helpsu suse it axess academic calendar stanford bulletin office of the registrar edmail stanfordwho stanfordyou login connect with us on facebook connect with us on twitter connect with us on youtube connect with us on flickr make a gift now
